### Создание фильма
# @no-redirect
POST http://localhost:8080/movies
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Game of Thrones",
  "producer": "Brian kirk",
  "director": "David Benioff",
  "release_year": 2011
}


### Редактирование фильма
PUT http://localhost:8080/movies/13
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Game of Thrones",
  "producer": "David Benioff",
  "director": "Brian Kirk",
  "release_year": 2011
}


### Удалить фильм
DELETE http://localhost:8080/movies/13
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
