### Создание бюджета
POST http://localhost:8080/movies/13/budget
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_movie": "13",
  "total_budget": 69000000.00,
  "fees_in_prod_country": 3800000.00,
  "fees_in_other": 22000000.00
}


### Редактирование бюджета
PUT http://localhost:8080/movies/13/budget
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_movie": "13",
  "total_budget": 60000000.00,
  "fees_in_prod_country": 2500000.00,
  "fees_in_other": 15000000.00
}


